## 2026-04-04 - Plugin sandbox functions silently return success on Figma API failures
- Fixed `scanTokenVariableBindings` (variableSync.ts L375): catch block now includes `error` field in the `token-variable-bindings-result` message so UI distinguishes "no bindings" from "API failed"
- Fixed `scanCanvasHeatmap` (heatmapScanning.ts L188): changed generic `{ type: 'error' }` to `{ type: 'canvas-heatmap-error', error }` so useHeatmap.ts can surface it immediately instead of waiting for the 30-second timeout
- Fixed `scanComponentCoverage` (heatmapScanning.ts L47): changed generic `{ type: 'error' }` to `{ type: 'component-coverage-error', error, correlationId }` so AnalyticsPanel's correlationId-based Promise resolution can detect failures

